title: Housing Inventory Estimate: Vacant Housing Units Held Off the Market and for Occasional Use in the South Census Region
notes: If the vacant unit is not for-rent or for-sale-only but is held for weekends or occasional use throughout the year, the unit is included in the category "for occasional use". Time-shared units are classified in this category if the vacant unit is not for-rent or for-sale-only, but held for use for an individual during the time of interview.
